amentary-trusts.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">testamentary trust<\/a><\/span><\/strong>\u00a0is a trust that is created after the grantor dies. Testamentary trusts are funded according to the terms specified in the grantor\u2019s last will and testament.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-d4b7cda e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"d4b7cda\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-c0251ac e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"c0251ac\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-83021d2 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"83021d2\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-62989e4 elementor-widget elementor-widget-button\" data-id=\"62989e4\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"button.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-button-wrapper\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<a class=\"elementor-button elementor-size-sm\" role=\"button\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-button-content-wrapper\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-button-text\">Question<\/span>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/span>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/a>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-f83a363 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"f83a363\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<h4 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">What is a charitable trust?<\/h4>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t